data.description: Gorgeous home in desirable Providence neighborhood. Natural hardwood and travertine floors; 10 FT tray ceilings; crown molding; large windows w/ wood blinds; ceiling fans; modern kitchen w/ granite counters, custom stone backsplash & stainless steel appliances; open floor plan & wood burning fireplace; MBR w/ walk-in closet; en-suite MBA w/double-sink, Sep shower & jet tub; large 5th BR/bonus Rm w/ full bath. Fenced backyard w/ covered patio, lush grass, auto sprinklers, & exterior lighting. 2 car garage.
